Commands sheet
Roles: A (Admin), U (User), G (User Group Leader).
Parameters:
PID: Player ID, player name followed of the last 4 digits of their Steam ID, Example: “InGameName#1234”.
Syntax: “command” “parameter”.
Example: /adult InGameName#1234
